Do Not Track
Internet browsers may have settings regarding tracking. Such settings are called “Do Not Track”. There are currently no standards for the Do Not Track signals or how to respond to them. As such, PF adheres to the standards set out in this Privacy Policy.
Governing Law
PF is operated in the United States; the Site and the App are intended for consumers in the United States. When we process personal data and information and personally identifying information in the United States, we follow United States data protection and privacy regulations.
Changes to Our Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to make changes to this Privacy Policy at any time. We will post revisions to this Privacy Policy, and the changes are effective when we post them on www.hyperspektiv.com. By continuing to use the Site and App after the effective date of those changes, you agree to be bound by the revised Privacy Policy.  If you do not accept all changes, please do not visit the Site and please discontinue use of and uninstall the App.